have the form \code{"CHR<sep>POS<sep>..."} (e.g. SCALLOP \code{"MarkerName"}).
\code{chr} and \code{pos} are extracted from the first two fields. This step runs
before the rsID lookup so that the extracted coordinates are available for
the bim join.
